{"tid":1466883,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不如我地聽日後日冷靜一吓先啦好嘛","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:33.000Z","uid":94290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b78ed23c7d1b17479389f6f4746f5d73c728c97e","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"知道大家都好嬲<br />\n但係我地係咪俾憤怒矇閉咗雙眼呢？<br />\n呢兩日大家情緒太激動 波動<br />\n好易俾對家trigger到 <br />\n例如琴日散水嘅問題<br />\n今日捉鬼 和理非嘅問題<br />\n我地自己都未諗好到底要行去邊個方向<br />\n不如襯18號之前 停一停<br />\n俾自己休息一吓 諗清楚<br />\n呢兩日對家都冇大動作就已經搞到我地四分五裂喇<br />\n講到底 呢次都係長期抗爭 再係咁落去唔係辦法<br />\n<br />\n講多句 大家係需要檢討 <br />\n請大家唔好好似支那大國咁玻璃心 <br />\n俾手足屌幾句 又話人地割你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd2c575e1f4f5288196fae05315e24a662c3d61","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"不完美"},{"pid":"cb710634205f5ab278af6f7fa0768c95e3c42ed9","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"可接受"},{"pid":"7df557531fb096fb2d79ffdcd670cdfc3d547e4a","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"需要改善"},{"pid":"0d33df5be8d4efb51afefdc3cfa4b0cbb2ca68b1","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"自推一"},{"pid":"f60677302c63b1575b5b1c4453a2f8b782dea895","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"自推二"},{"pid":"4822aa6d8d70a5502b49a0cc87d27ca4241f2a2e","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"白推三"},{"pid":"fc1869e425a513f1269736f28e830820faced236","tid":1466883,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a469a997eb1226112ef2f3cabb6534f80bdca84","tid":14